Module org.example.proyecto
Package org.example.proyecto.model.booking

Class BookingDataHelper

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.model.booking.BookingDataHelper
public class BookingDataHelper extends Object
Helper class for booking data that includes additional information such as email and housing name. This class encapsulates a BookingDTO object along with an email address and housing name.
Since:
2024-05-28
Author:
Rafael
